description.en: The Obee Network social platform will be the first social product for ordinary users to enter the blockchain era. It is an incentive platform based on blockchain social networking and has built a complete decentralized social network. Let users see the creations, forums, hot posts, applications and movies of users around the world on Obee Network. Let social without boundaries, and you can share wonderful moments with other users anytime and anywhere. Obee Network will also better serve the defi ecosystem and become a communication bridge for defi projects.
